Jordan 12 Retro Low Easter (2021)
results.story: The Air Jordan 12 Retro Low ‘Easter’ gives the classic low-top a spring-ready makeover. The upper is constructed from stitched white leather and fortified with signature tall mudguards in matching white tumbled leather. Metallic iridescent detailing makes its way to the sneaker’s upper eyelets and a quarter panel overlays. Webbing pull tabs at the heel are decorated with standard Jordan branding elements. Underfoot, an icy translucent outsole is fitted with a visible shank plate and herringbone traction pods.

results.name: Nike Air Tuned Max Celery
results.story: The 2021 edition of the Nike Air Tuned Max OG ‘Celery’ represents the first ever reissue of the 1999 runner. The build is faithful to the original, featuring a breathable black mesh upper with tonal TPU detailing, coppery synthetic leather overlays and an iridescent green finish on the molded collar. On the heel, a gold embroidered Swoosh is accompanied by five white dots — a nod to the Nike Alpha Project and a marker of performance-driven innovation. Lightweight cushioning is provided by a sculpted black Phylon midsole with a visible Tuned Air unit under the heel.

Collina Strada x Wmns Classic Leather Legacy 'Call Mom'
results.story: Launching as part of a capsule collection with Hillary Taymour’s fashion brand, the Collina Strada x Reebok women’s Classic Leather Legacy ‘Call Mom’ features a sustainable build covered in brushstroke detailing. 40% recycled vegan leather is utilized on the upper, secured with laces and lined in textile made with 100% recycled polyester. A woven tag on the lateral eyestay displays Collina branding, while ‘Call Mom’ is inscribed across the heel tabs of the left and right shoe. Lightweight cushioning comes courtesy of a plush EVA midsole.

results.name: adidas Dame 7 Fine China
results.story: The adidas Dame 7 ‘Fine China’ replicates the look of porcelain tableware with red and blue prints depicting dragons, leaves and clouds. The ornate designs are applied to the tongue, heel, Lightstrike midsole and translucent rubber outsole, while the majority of the sneaker’s textile upper is rendered in a clean white finish. Additional embellishments include Damian Lillard’s personal logo embroidered on the tongue and ‘Gift to the World’ inscribed on contrasting red insoles.

results.name: Team Hustle D10 GS 'Black Game Royal'
adidas Dame 7 Fire Of Greatness
results.story: The adidas Dame 7 ‘Fire Inside’ treats Damian Lillard’s signature shoe to a bold monochromatic finish inspired by Chinese lanterns. An integrated lacing system secures the breathable textile upper, lined with internal cushioning pods and reinforced with tonal synthetic leather at the toe and heel. ‘Fire of Greatness’ is inscribed on the lace keeper stitched atop the tongue, while the sockliner is marked with text that reads ‘Gift to the World.’ A full-length Lightstrike midsole in a matching Solar Red hue provides a combination of stability and energy return.

results.name: Nike Air Max Tailwind V Skepta
results.story: The Skepta x Nike Air Max Tailwind 5 ‘Bright Blue’ reunites the Swoosh with the London-based grime artist for a fifth collaborative go-round. Inspired by the natural world, the lifestyle runner features a sublimated butterfly-wing print on a turquoise mesh upper borrowed from the 2007 Tailwind V Plus. A chrome Swoosh recalls the 2019 SK Shox, while a thermographic heel counter gives the nod to the cover art from Skepta’s 2019 album, ‘Ignorance Is Bliss.’ The sneaker rides on a Phylon midsole with visible Max Air cushioning in the forefoot and heel.

results.name: Amoeba Music x Nice Kicks x 992 Made in USA 'Teal Black'
results.story: The Amoeba Music x Nice Kicks x New Balance 992 Made in USA ‘Teal Black’ is taken from a larger collaborative collection from the like-minded sneaker and music retailers. New Balance’s retro runner gets a colorful update inspired by Amoeba’s neon signage, highlighted by a turquoise mesh upper with a tonal forefoot suede overlay. Contrasting black suede is utilized on the saddle, while cream-hued suede wraps around the heel. ‘Peace’ and ‘Music’ are inscribed across the back heel of each shoe. The sneaker sits atop a two-tone ABZORB midsole.

results.name: Amoeba Music x Nice Kicks x 992 Made in USA 'Grey Yellow'
results.story: The Amoeba Music x Nice Kicks x New Balance 992 Made in USA ‘Grey Yellow’ is one of two collaborative colorways that make up the centerpiece in a capsule collection from the music and sneaker retailers. Inspired by Amoeba’s colorful logo, this pair takes the iconic grey colorway of the 992 and adds bright bursts of yellow to the forefoot and collar. The traditional mesh and suede build is secured with woven laces in a mint green hue, a color that’s repeated on the ‘Peace’ and ‘Music’ inscriptions that adorn each heel.

Bodega x Vault OG Style 36 LX 'High Note'
results.story: Celebrating the 15th anniversary of the Boston-based retailer, the Bodega x Vault OG Style 36 LX ‘High Note’ projects a ‘warped take on luxury.’ Black suede is utilized on the upper, along with tonal tumbled leather overlays and mismatched suede side stripes in white and tan. Elevated details include tortoise-shell eyelets, leather laces, a coated checkerboard-print tongue and a leather-lined interior in hot pink. ‘Bodega’ is stamped in a repeating pattern on the off-white rubber midsole.

results.name: adidas DON Issue 2 Dragons and Clouds
results.story: The adidas D.O.N. Issue #2 ‘Kumu Clouds & Dragon’ enlivens Donovan Mitchell’s second signature shoe with a Japanese-inspired print throughout the textile upper. An engineered cord lacing system provides a feeling of lockdown, while a molded heel counter hugs the back of the foot for enhanced rearfoot stability. The low-top is mounted on a responsive Bounce midsole, supported by a translucent rubber outsole that wraps up the medial toe for added durability and traction.

results.name: Air Max 95 Recraft GS 'White Game Royal'
Reebok Classic Leather Legacy ASAP Nast
results.story: Crafted in partnership with the Harlem rapper, the A$AP Nast x Reebok Classic Leather Legacy ‘Sandy Taupe’ features neutral tones on an upper crafted from a blend of textile twill and suede. Leather side stripes are rendered in dark brown, while contrasting pops of lavender land on the sneaker’s looped eyelets and one of two heel overlays. An exposed foam tongue accentuates the vintage running-shoe aesthetic. Lightweight cushioning is provided by a stacked EVA midsole.

results.name: Suede Classic 'Mono Iced - Aruba Blue'
results.story: The PUMA Suede Classic ‘Mono Iced’ applies a simple one-note color scheme to a vintage hoops shoe that dates back to 1968. A chilly Aruba Blue finish floods the minimalist suede upper, accented with perforated detailing around the tonal Formstrip. Additional branding hits take the form of a debossed PUMA wordmark on the tongue tag and lateral quarter panel. A semi-translucent rubber cupsole anchors the low-profile silhouette in the same icy hue.

Dejounte Murray x Two WXY 'Personal Journey'
results.story: The Dejounte Murray x New Balance Two WXY ‘Personal Journey’ is clad in vibrant hues inspired by the NBA point guard. The performance hoops shoe is built for modern players who compete at both ends of the court, featuring a flexible upper crafted from Kinetic Stitch textile. Two WXY branding is displayed on a fused no-sew tongue, which combines with a padded mid-cut collar to deliver enhanced comfort. The sneaker rides on a responsive FuelCell foam midsole, reinforced by a data-driven rubber outsole and a midfoot shank borrowed from the OMN1S.

Forum 84 Low 'White Crew Green'
results.story: The adidas Forum 84 Low ‘White Crew Green’ offers a simple two-tone colorway of the retro hoops shoe, featuring legacy details that include the adjustable ankle strap and X-shaped overlay. A subtle Cloud White finish is executed on the leather upper, accented with hairy suede three-stripes in a lush green hue. A more subdued shade of olive green is applied to the sneaker’s terry lining and rubber outsole. The latter supports an off-white rubber midsole, fitted with an EVA wedge that’s exposed on the medial side.
